This year one of my goals was to lean more into random hobbies & creative outlets. Lately I’ve been into floral arrangements & thought it would be fun to thrift some vases & make Valentine’s Day bouquets!!!! 

All info is on the graphic !
Venmo @ autumnbrea to preorder 
$30 for local pickup 
$35 for local delivery !

Includes a bouquet (10-15 stems) , a vase, & a little note card if you want to send a message with it :) 💌

Perfect Vday gift for your boyfriend/girlfriend/parents/friends/yourself ;) 🌷 (& a gift to me by ordering bc rent is expensive lol 🤩)

Taking orders from now until Feb 12th! Dm if you have any questions!

My love for 2 years now! & counting !

“Home” has been changing a lot lately with my best friends / roomates moving out post grad & I don’t know how to feel about it !!!!!!! Living with them has been the most sweet, special time that I will cherish forever. ✨ Change is wonderful and beautiful & allows so much room for new wonderful & beautiful things, but it can also leave a little bit of an ache behind. Reminder that change is difficult on everyone & you can feel 2 contradicting feelings at the same time!! Feeling excited and hopeful for the future, and a bit achy and bittersweet about the past. Thankful for this home & these walls that have been filled with so much community & laughter & love & im just as excited for there to be plenty more of that soon🏡 🤍🤍🤍✨✨
Feelin grateful & full of lots of love (& seafood) 🫶🏻🦪🦀
